        helicopters, UAVs, balloons, or similar aerial means. The information typically gathered encompasses aerial photography, Lidar, 
        remote sensing (harnessing diverse electromagnetic spectrum bands, both visible and invisible, such as infrared, gamma, or ultraviolet).
    </p>
